{
  "chapter": "066",
  "title": "伍子胥列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "家世蒙难",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国人，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span>长叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍尚</span>。他的祖先叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍举</span>，因直言进谏事奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄王</span>而显达，所以其后代在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国很有名望。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span>，费<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少傅</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不忠。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">迎娶</span>妻子，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>美貌，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>飞奔回来报告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国女子绝美，王可自己<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">娶</span>了，再给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>另外<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">娶</span>妻。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>于是亲自娶了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>，对她极为宠爱，生了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚昭王\">轸（楚昭王）</span>。另给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>娶了别的妇人。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>既已凭借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>讨好<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>，便离开<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>而事奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>。他担心<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一旦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>去世而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>即位，会<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>自己，便借机向王进谗言中伤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>国女子，不受<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>宠爱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>渐渐疏远<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>去驻守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>，防备边兵。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "不久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>又日夜向王进言<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的短处说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>因<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>的缘故，不能没有怨望，希望王稍自戒备。自从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span>，统兵在外，结交<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，将要入都作乱了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>便召来<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太傅</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>审问。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>知道是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>面前谗毁<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，就说：\"王为何因谗贼<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">小臣</span>而疏远骨肉之亲呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>说：\"王今天若不制止，此事就会坐大。王将被擒获。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>大怒，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>，并派<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">城父</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">奋扬</span>前去<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。途中还未到达，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">奋扬</span>就派人先告知<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>赶快逃走，不然将被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>逃奔到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>国。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "逃亡入吴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无忌</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>有两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，都很贤能，不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，必为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国祸患。可以用他们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲做人质来召他们来，不然必为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国之患。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>派使者对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>说：\"你能招来你的两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>就生，不能就死。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍奢</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍尚\">尚（伍尚）</span>为人仁厚，一召必来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>为人刚戾忍辱，能成大事，他看出来就会一起被擒，形势所迫，必定不会来。\"王不听，派人去召两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>说：\"来，我让你们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲活命；不来，现在就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍奢\">奢（伍奢）</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍尚</span>想前往，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国召我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>，并非想让我们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲生还，而是怕有漏网之鱼后成祸患，所以用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲做人质，诈召两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>到了，则<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父子</span>都会死。这对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲的死有什么好处？去了反让仇不能报。不如奔逃他国，借力来雪<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>之耻，一同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">被灭</span>，就毫无作为了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍尚</span>说：\"我知道去终究不能保全<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲的性命。但憾恨<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲召我以求生而我不去，将来又不能雪耻，终为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>所笑。\"对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>说：\"你可以走了！你能报<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>之仇，我将归去赴死。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍尚\">尚（伍尚）</span>既已就擒，使者来捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>张开<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓</span>，搭上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢</span>对着使者，使者不敢上前，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>于是逃亡。听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>国，就前往投奔他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍奢\">奢（伍奢）</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>逃亡，说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>将苦于战事了。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍尚</span>到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>都，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>一并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍奢\">奢（伍奢）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍尚\">尚（伍尚）</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>国之后，遇上<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>有<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">华氏</span>之乱，就和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>一同奔走到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国人对他们很友好。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>又到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷公</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>既然与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国友善，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国信任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>能做我的内应，我从外<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打它，必能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>后就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>便返回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。事情未能成就，恰好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>因私事想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>随从，随从知道了他的计谋，就告发到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">定公</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子产</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：太子建\">建（太子建）</span>有一个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>害怕，就和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>一同逃奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。到了昭关，昭关守卒想抓捕他们。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>只好和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>独身步行奔逃，几乎不能逃脱。追兵在后。到了江边，江上有一个<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">渔父</span>乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>，知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>情势紧急，就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>渡过江。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>渡过江后，解下身上的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>说：\"这把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>值<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>，用它赠给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>老。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>老说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的法令，捉到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>的赏粟<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万石</span>，爵至<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">执珪</span>，岂只值<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>呢！\"不接受。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>还未到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国就病倒了，停在中途，沿途乞食。到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，正是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span>执政，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>担任将军。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>就通过<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>求见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "助吴破楚",
      "text": "过了很久，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>因其边邑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">锺离</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国边邑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卑梁</span>氏都养蚕，两家的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>争桑叶相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>大怒，以致两国举兵相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻克</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">锺离</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">居巢</span>而归。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>劝说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打破</span>。希望再派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王说：\"那<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父兄</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀戮</span>，他劝王<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，是想借此报自家的仇罢了。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>未必能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻破</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>怀有内心之志，想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>王而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，不便以外事劝说，就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">专诸</span>引荐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>，自己退而和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>一起在野外耕种。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>去世。当初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>夺走<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>所生的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚昭王\">轸（楚昭王）</span>，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚昭王\">轸（楚昭王）</span>竟然被立为后嗣，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span>趁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>有丧事，派两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>率兵前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>发兵截断了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵归路，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵不得回。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国内空虚，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子光</span>便命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">专诸</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，这就是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王阖庐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>既已即位，得意之时，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍员（伍子胥）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">行人</span>官，与之共谋国事。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀它的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郤宛</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯州犁</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯州犁</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯嚭</span>逃奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>也任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。先前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span>所派的两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，归路被阻不得返回。后来听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王僚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>，就率其兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">投降</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>他们在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">舒</span>地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，便兴师与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍胥（伍子胥）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯嚭</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻克</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">舒</span>地，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒获</span>从前反叛<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国的两位<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>。顺势想攻到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都，将军<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙武</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>已疲惫，不可，暂且等待。\"于是班师。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">灊</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>越国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公子囊瓦</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍员（伍子胥）</span>迎<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">居巢</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "入郢鞭尸",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王阖庐</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙武</span>说：\"当初<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都不可攻入，现在怎么样？\"二人回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">囊瓦</span>贪婪，而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>两国都怨恨他。王如果一定要大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，必须先得到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>两国的支持才行。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>听从了，倾全国之兵与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>一起<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>军夹<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>列阵。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span>请求率兵随行，王不听，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span>就率其部属<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子常</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>逃走，奔到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>乘胜向前，经过五次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗，攻到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">己卯</span>日，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>出逃。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">庚辰</span>日，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>逃亡，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦</span>；盗贼<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span>王，王又逃到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郧</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郧公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲，我<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，不也是可以的吗！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郧公</span>怕其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>王，与王奔走到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">随</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">随</span>国，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">随</span>人说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉川</span>一带的，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国全部<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了他们。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">随</span>人想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>王，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">綦</span>把王藏起来，自己冒充王去应对。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">随</span>人占卜把王交给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，不吉，于是谢绝<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，不交王。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">伍员（伍子胥）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申包胥</span>有交情，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>逃亡时，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申包胥\">包胥（申包胥）</span>说：\"我必定要颠覆<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申包胥\">包胥（申包胥）</span>说：\"我必定要保存<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。\"等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>寻找<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>。没找到，就挖开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>的坟墓，拖出他的尸体，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span>了三百下，才停下来。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申包胥</span>逃亡在山中，派人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>说：\"您这样报仇，也太过分了吧！我听说，人多众者能胜天，但天定也能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打破</span>人。现在您从前是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子，亲自北面事奉过他，如今做到了<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">僇</span>辱死人，这难道不是违背<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天道</span>到极点了吗！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>说：\"代我向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申包胥</span>致谢，就说：我日暮途远，所以倒行而逆施。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">申包胥</span>奔赴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国告急，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国求救。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国不答应。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：申包胥\">包胥（申包胥）</span>立在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国朝廷，昼夜痛哭，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七天</span>七夜哭声不绝。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀公</span>怜悯他，说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国虽无道，有这样的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子，怎可使它灭亡呢！\"于是派<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百乘</span>救<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六月</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">稷</span>地<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵。正值<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王久留<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国寻找<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span>逃归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为王。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>听说后，放<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">释</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国而回国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>逃走，于是逃奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭王</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>有内乱，就再度进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫概</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">堂谿</span>，成为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">堂谿</span>氏。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>又与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王才回国。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子夫差</span>率兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻取</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番</span>地。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>害怕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国再大举进攻，就离开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>，迁都于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄀</span>。当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>凭借<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙武</span>的谋略，西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，北威<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，南使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>人<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">服</span>从。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国做相。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "谏阻伐齐",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>迎<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">姑苏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军，射伤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>脚指，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>军退却。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>因伤病重将死，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子夫差</span>说：\"你忘了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>你<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>答道：\"不敢忘。\"当晚，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>死去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>即位为王后，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯嚭</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span>，操练<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗射技。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夫湫</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>就带残兵<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千人</span>退守在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>山上，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：文种\">种（文种）</span>厚币贿赂<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>以请和，请求托国为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣妾</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王打算答应。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>进谏说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王能吃苦耐劳。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>他，将来必定后悔。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王不听，采用<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>的计策，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>讲和。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐景公</span>死了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>争宠，新<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>年幼软弱，就兴师向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>进谏说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>食不兼味，吊死问病，正是想有所作为。此人不死，必为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国之患。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国，犹如人有腹心之疾。而王不先解决<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国却去致力<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，不也谬误吗！\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王不听，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">艾陵</span>大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>师，于是威服<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>而归。越发疏远<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>的谋略。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王将北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>采用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子贡</span>的谋略，就率其众去助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，并把重宝献给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>几次受<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国贿赂后，对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国格外喜爱信任，日夜向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王进言。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王信用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>的计策。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>进谏说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国是腹心之病，如今却信它的浮辞诈伪而贪<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，如同得到石田，毫无用处。而且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span>的诰辞说：'有颠倒违逆不恭顺的人，劓鼻根绝<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>除，使无遗孓，不让坏种子在这城邑繁衍。'这是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商</span>朝兴盛的原因。希望王放<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">释</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国而先除<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国；不然，将来后悔也来不及。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王不听，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>临行前，对他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>说：\"我多次进谏王，王不采纳，我现在看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国的灭亡了。你和<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国一同灭亡，没有好处。\" 就把他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>托付给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲍牧</span>，然后回到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国复命。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "赐死抉眼",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>既已与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>有隔阂，便进谗言说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>为人刚强暴戾，少恩猜忌，他的怨望恐怕会酿成大祸。前日王想<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>认为不可，王最终<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>之而建大功。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>以自己计谋不被采用为耻，反而怨望。如今王又要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>专横强谏，阻挠诋毁王的行事，只是希望<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>以证明自己的计谋罢了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>亲自出征，倾全国武力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>谏言不被采用，就借故辞谢，假装有病不随行。王不可不戒备，这样引起祸患并不困难。而且<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>派人暗中窥伺他，他出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国时，就把他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>托付给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">鲍氏</span>。作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>，在朝内不得意，对外依靠<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，自认为是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">谋臣</span>，如今不被任用，常常怏怏怨望。希望王早作打算。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王说：\"没有您的话，我也怀疑他。\"就派使者赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>一把属镂<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>用这把剑自尽吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>仰天长叹道：\"唉！谗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>作乱，王反而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀我。我使你<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲称霸。在你还未即位时，诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>争立，我以死争于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>前，你才几乎得以立为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。你既已即位，想分<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国给我，我反不敢奢望。然而如今你听信谀<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>之言<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>害长者。\"就告诉他的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>说：\"一定要在我墓上种<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">梓</span>树，使它可做为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">器</span>；挖出我的眼睛挂在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东门</span>上，让我看到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>寇入<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。\"于是自刎而死。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王听说后大怒，就把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>尸体装进鸱夷<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">革</span>囊，投入江中。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国人怜悯他，在江边建立祠堂，因此称之为胥山。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "吴终灭亡",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王既已<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">鲍氏</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span>而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阳生</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王想讨伐乱贼，不胜而去。其后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王召<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>两国之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">橐皋</span>相会。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">明年</span>，又在北方的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄池</span>大会<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，以号令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>室。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">打破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>兵。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王听说后，于是回师，派使者用重币与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>讲和。后来<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">句践</span>终于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>；并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太宰</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伯嚭\">嚭（伯嚭）</span>，因为他不忠于其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，而对外接受重贿，与自己结党营私。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "白公之乱",
      "text": "当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>一起逃亡的从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太子建</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>，当时在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夫差</span>的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>想召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叶公</span>进谏说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>好勇而暗中网罗敢死之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，大概有私心！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>不听。于是召回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>，使他居于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的边邑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄢</span>地，号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>既已回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，怨<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>害其<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>，就暗中豢养敢死之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>图谋报复<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国。归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五年（时长）</span>后，请求<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>答应了。军队未发而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>求救。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>去救援，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>结盟而返。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>愤怒地说：\"仇人不是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国，而是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>亲自磨<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>，有人问：\"拿来做什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>说：\"想用它来<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>听说后，笑着说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>不过像一枚蛋罢了，能做什么。\""
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "",
      "text": "其后<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：白公胜\">胜（白公胜）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭击</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子西</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司马</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子綦</span>于朝廷。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>说：\"不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>王，不行。\"于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">劫</span>持王到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高府</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>的从者<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">屈固</span>背负<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>逃到昭<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>的宫中。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叶公</span>听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>作乱，率国人<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>之徒被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击败</span>，逃到山中，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">俘虏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>，问他<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>尸体在何处，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>不说，将要被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹杀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>说：\"事成为卿，不成而被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span>，本是我的职分。\"终究不肯告诉尸身所在。于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">烹</span>杀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">石乞</span>，而寻求<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠王</span>，重新让他即位。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：怨毒对于人真是厉害啊！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>尚不能把怨毒施行到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>下，何况同列之人呢！倘若当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伍子胥</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍奢\">奢（伍奢）</span>一同就死，和<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蝼蚁</span>有什么区别。他舍弃小义，雪了大耻，名垂于后世，可悲啊！当<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">子胥（伍子胥）</span>困窘于江边、途中乞食的时候，他心中岂曾一刻忘记过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都呢？所以能隐忍以成就功名，不是烈<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>谁能做到这种地步？<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白公</span>如果不<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，那么他的功绩与谋略也是不可胜数的啊！"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "谗人没有穷尽，扰乱四方之国。 可叹那<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">伍氏</span>一族，遭此凶恶灾祸！ <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：伍子胥\">员（伍子胥）</span>独能忍受耻辱，志在报复冤毒。 称霸<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国起兵出师，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>追击溃兵。 <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">鞭</span>尸以雪大耻，抉眼却弃<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>行。"
    }
